    "description": {
      "value": "<p>You create one hakutou, a glowing white cross-shaped dagger that weighs nothing and deals 1d4 piercing damage, as well as 3d4 holy damage that is not multiplied on critical hits. The weapon is considered to be a dagger, and benefits from modifiers you may have to such a weapon.<br><br>If it hits an evil creature, a hakutou creates a brilliant glow for a moment. If it hits a non-evil creature, it deals no damage. In either case, once it hits, it disintegrates.</p>\n\n<hr><p><b>Empower:</b> Spend 3 Chakra to create an additional hakutou (up to 1 per 3 levels or 5 total, whichever is lower).</p>\n\n",
